Request 1 by gayporwave
Guild Wars 2 (Video Game) 

General DNWs: Issuefic, mentions of het/background het canon or not (unless otherwise specified), songfic, plotless fluff, major character death, requested characters written as asexuals, non-standard canon levels of homophobia (I'm pretty lax with this I generally just mean that even if the canon has homophobia I don't want it taken to the next level/a gaybashing fic, I'd generally prefer homophobia not be the main focus of the fic.)

Smut DNWs: Bodily fluids, fisting, underage sex, ageplay, detailed kink negotiation, safewords for scenes that don't involve consent play, excessive cum.

