Dorus - Just how much autonomy does he have? Is he just a puppet, 100% controlled by Sendor, or can he act on his own at all? What's it like to live without a soul?

Sendor - How did he find out about the black crystal sword in the first place? Or, how did he meet Shena? What was it that brought them together?

Shena - What's a kerim? They're described as "elves of ice," but that's not much to go on. Why was it illegal for her to be in a relationship with Sendor? How did she deal with losing her son and Sendor all in one go (either when Dorus died the first time or second time)?

